            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>shredded red cabbage</strong>, <strong>mayo </strong>and <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> in a separate bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>red cabbage slaw</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice the <strong>spring onions</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1679315577568-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1679315577568-x400.jpg",
