          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer the <strong>chicken</strong> to kitchen paper and wipe the pan clean</p><p>Return the pan to a medium heat and add the <strong>miso paste</strong> and <strong>chipotle</strong> <strong>paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with a splash of <strong>water</strong></p><p>Whisk until fully combined and cook for 2 min or until thickened and warmed through</p>",
